#PROGRAM OBJECTIVES 

1. The program seeks to track anormalies in VOLUME over time traded per stock from the largest banks in South Africa. 
2. Direction of the Volume per stock, BUY or SELL.
3. Distribution of the Volume traded,with respect to time and calender month. 
4. Real Market sentiment




DATA
1. Some Banks provide this information freely through paid API connection. 
2. SBG securities has been helpful with manuel datasets. 
3. Efficient tracker NEEDS 



Which Stock to track volume ? 

1. A stock with less focus from institutional buyers, pension funds
2. A stock with market capitalisation of less 10B why ? Anormalies would be easier to track and identify 

